body: If you think your son or daughter can do better on the SAT I agree Score increases are the norm not the exception when students practice under the direction of a knowledgeable tutor I have extensive experience helping students prepare for the SAT and heres what youll notice about my lessons  EFFICIENT My oneonone tutoring does what a classroom course never could tailor the material to the individuals strengths and weaknesses Initial diagnostic testing and continual stepbystep assessment of each students progress are essential to an effective lesson plan I know the test backwards and forwards so I can focus test prep efforts to achieve the best possible results  UNDERSTANDING A word of warning I give plenty of homework and I continually remind students that they MUST do it if they want to succeed Beyond that though I will absolutely never bully a student While a classroom course will bore some students and leave others feeling unwelcome and hopelessly behind my lessons will give every student the confidence to tackle the test headon  FLEXIBLE Whether youre looking for something indepth and longterm or just to brush up in the few weeks before the exam I can accommodate your needs I can travel to your home or meet somewhere mutually convenient and our lesson times will suit your schedule and your budget  AFFORDABLE The fact that the Princeton Review charges 135 an hour for oneonone SAT tutoring should convince you of the value of this service As an individual I can afford to charge just a fraction of that price only 60 an hour  Im so confident that youll love what you see that I offer a free first lesson to all of my clients Call 6173209321 to schedule yours today      its NOT ok to contact this poster with services or other commercial interests    PostingID3410137505     Copyright copy 2012 craigslist inc  terms of use  privacy policy  feedback forum
